R.P., Plaintiff,
v.
P.K., Defendant-Movant. M-306/307/308/309/310/311 September Term 2018
081233 Supreme Court of New Jersey. NOVEMBER 16, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the miscellaneous motions to withdraw exhibit attached to papers on M-1575-17 (M-306), for primary residential custody and other relief (M-310), and to reprimand and remove trial court judge and other relief (M-311) are denied; and it is further

ORDERED that the motions to expand the record (M-307/308/309) are denied.
